net.jini.lookup

Class LookupCacheImpl.ServiceItemReg

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.jini.lookup.LookupCacheImpl.ServiceItemReg
  • Enclosing class:
    LookupCacheImpl

    static final class LookupCacheImpl.ServiceItemReg
extends Object
    Used in the LookupCache. For each LookupCache, there is a HashMap that maps ServiceId to a ServiceItemReg. The ServiceItemReg class helps track where the ServiceItem comes from.
